<D>__{so they travel around from place to place and preach?}
<C>__{jackson}
<D>__{we got us a tent, forty two feet across, eighteen feet at center, hundred and ten foldin' chairs. circuit's eleven towns, covers all 'a hasset county and most 'a weller county. i expect that upon completion of my military service i will be joinin' said ministry.}
<C>__{upham}
<D>__{what about the captain? where's he from?}
